      <!-- Text Block -->
      <div class="about center">
        <h3>Purpose</h3>
        <p class="project__description">
          Uploader is a relatively simple concept, but it fills a
          very important gap in current file sharing methods. The
          objective of this project was to solve the real-world problem
          that is transferring large files between devices, with relative
          ease. Applications like Dropbox or Gmail either have significant
          client applications or significant file size limitations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about center">
        <p class="project__description">
          Uploader allows for an arbitrary large file to be uploaded to a
          server, which responds with a download link containing a unique
          file token. This link can then be shared through any medium and
          downloaded on the new device.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Block -->
      <section id="projects" class="section projects">
        <div class="projects__grid">
